'''lactam'''
#{{chemistry}} any of a class of [[cyclic]] [[amide]]s, that are the [[nitrogen]] [[analog]]s of [[lactone]]s, formed by heating [[amino acid]]s; the [[tautomeric]] [[enol]] forms are known as [[lactim]]s
